com.serena.dmclient.objects
Class PseudoBranches

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.PseudoBranches

public class PseudoBranches
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates predefined Dimensions pseudo branches. Pseudo branches are used to define replication configurations.

Note: <ALL_...> pseudo branches are not currently supported for local replication. You will need to explicitly state the branch names to be replicated.

ALL_LOCAL_BRANCHES

public static final VersionBranch ALL_LOCAL_BRANCHES
The ALL_LOCAL_BRANCHES pseudo branch. Selecting this branch ensures that all named branches in the master database site that are owned by that site are replicated to subordinates.
